data.description: Location Location Location! Minutes from Oaklawn & in the heart of Hot Springs, this charming family home is waiting for you to make memories for years to come.  4 BR (downstairs can be 4th bdrm),  3.5 bath with plenty of room for everyone.  Enjoy the beautiful landscape of a quiet large backyard, 3 car garage, sunroom, breakfast room, large living room & dining.  Enjoy the outdoors with a walkout balcony from the main bedroom. Downstairs has an outdoor walkout which can also work as a private apartment. Original hardwood floors and crown molding throughout the house add so much character. The house is equipped with solar panels which will greatly save on energy bills (as low as $12/mo). Downstairs unit was new 2019 and a new coil and fan motor were replaced in 2018 in the upstairs unit. Roof was replaced in 2019. New water heaters in 2020. Storm windows replaced in last 5 years. Welcome home!
